50:51.285 --> 50:53.267
And did you want to?

50:53.287 --> 50:54.508
We actually have looked at the framework.

50:56.394 --> 51:00.398
strongly support their framework, which is why we said it is part of kind of like our ideal curriculum.

51:00.878 --> 51:10.086
